sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant UI as Programme Edit Page
    participant LW as Livewire Component
    participant DB as Database

    User->>UI: Open create/update programme page
    UI->>LW: mount(programme)
    LW->>DB: Load programme (if existing) + institute/module options
    DB-->>LW: Existing values and options
    LW-->>UI: Render programme form

    User->>UI: Change institute
    UI->>LW: updatedInstituteId(value)
    LW->>DB: Filter available modules by institute
    DB-->>LW: Allowed modules
    LW-->>UI: Re-render module multiselect

    User->>UI: Save programme
    UI->>LW: save()
    LW->>DB: Validate and insert/update programme + module links
    DB-->>LW: Persisted programme
    LW-->>UI: Success toast (new: redirect to edit page)
